      "x": 348, "y": 382,
      "width": 584, "height": 64,
      "text": "CascadedRouter — cascaded_router.py [506L]\nTier 0: MemoryResolver | Tier 1: LRU | Tier 2: Redis hash | Tier 3: VectorSemanticCache (pgvector)\nTier 4: FastRouter (regex) | Tier 5: LLM Cascade (Haiku→Sonnet→Opus)\n+ IntentRouter legado em fallback paralelo",
